Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:32.25,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962.4,664.2)\1c&HA19AF8&}美羽與稻葉④
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,吶吶  來拍個照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  要拍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  再往上一點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  這下就變醜了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再右一點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.09,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對對  就這角度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就像這樣  跟我擺同樣的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你能擺個看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,OK  另外  表情很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在我說好之前  絕對絕對不能按快門哦
